2024-07-14 07:08:16 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1720940896,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"5.157.33.98","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (X11; Linux i686; rv:114.0) Gecko\/20100101 Firefox\/114.0","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":10078,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"10059","cat_id":"100","project_id":"1486","nick":"Joanna","content":"Hi,\r\n\r\nI just visited studioatrium.pl and wondered if you'd ever thought about having an engaging video to explain what you do?\r\n\r\nOur prices start from just $195.\r\n\r\nWe have produced over 500 videos to date and work with both non-animated and animated formats:\r\n\r\nNon-animated example:\r\nhttps:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=bA2DyChM4Oc\r\n\r\nAnimated example:\r\nhttps:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=JG33_MgGjfc\r\n\r\nLet me know if you're interested in learning more and\/or have any questions.\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\nJoanna\r\n\r\nUnsubscribe: https:\/\/removeme.click\/ev\/unsubscribe.php?d=studioatrium.pl","create_date":"2024-07-14 07:08:16","modify_date":"2024-07-14 07:08:16","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2580015},"entity_changes":false}
